          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EXTB"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The used beam originates from 8 degree",
                "scattering by a thin Be target of the primary 592 MeV",
                "proton beam, which is pulsed at a frequency of 51 MHz.",
                "It is focused on a Cu degrader, purified by a",
                "deflecting magnet and focused on the target position.",
                "To avoid the influence of the beam polarisation (42%)",
                "was rotated in a superconducting solenoid from the",
                "vertical direction into the horizontal scattering",
                "plane."
              ]
            },
